# PKDisbursementError.Code.unsupportedCardError

**Case**

The framework doesn’t support the card the individual presented.

## Declaration

```swift
case unsupportedCardError
```

## Error codes

- **PKDisbursementError.Code.recipientContactInvalidError**: The recipient’s contact information wasn’t valid.
- **PKDisbursementError.Code.unknownError**: An unknown error occurred.
